OL,3,CSouth Scotland: The race for a place
OL,4,Con the regional list
OL,6,FThe South Scotland region for the
OL,7,FScottish Parliament covers the whole
OL,8,Fof the Scottish Borders and Dumfries
OL,9,Fand Galloway as well as southern
OL,10,FAyrshire and parts of South
OL,11,FLanarkshire.
OL,13,FWhat is the Regional List?
OL,15,FHolyrood's voting system divides the
OL,16,Fcountry into eight regions.
OL,18,FPeople in South Scotland will elect
OL,19,Fseven MSPs using their peach-coloured
OL,20,Fballot paper.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/19
