OL,3,CSouth Scotland: The race for a place
OL,4,Con the regional list
OL,6,FHow does it work?
OL,8,FWhen you go to your local polling
OL,9,Fstation to vote on Thursday, May 7,
OL,10,Fyou will be handed two ballot papers.
OL,12,FOn the regional list ballot, or peach
OL,13,Fballot, you vote for a party, rather
OL,14,Fthan a candidate.
OL,16,FThere are 17 parties and independent
OL,17,Fcandidates standing for election in
OL,18,FSouth Scotland.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/19
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
