OL,3,CSouth Scotland: The race for a place
OL,4,Con the regional list
OL,6,FOn the constituency ballot, the lilac
OL,7,Fcoloured one, you vote for the
OL,8,Fcandidate you want to represent you.
OL,9,FOur region has four constituencies.
OL,11,FIn the Borders, the Ettrick, Roxburgh
OL,12,Fand Berwickshire constituency covers
OL,13,Ftowns including Eyemouth, Kelso, St
OL,14,FBoswells, Selkirk, Hawick and
OL,15,FNewcastleton.
OL,17,FThe Midlothian South, Tweeddale and
OL,18,FLauderdale constituency covers towns
OL,19,Fincluding Lauder, Melrose, Galashiels,
OL,20,FWalkerburn, Innerleithen and Peebles.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/19
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
