OL,3,CSouth Scotland: The race for a place
OL,4,Con the regional list
OL,6,FIn Dumfries and Galloway, the
OL,7,FDumfriesshire constituency covers
OL,8,Ftowns including Gretna, Moffat, Annan,
OL,9,FLockerbie, Langholm and the eastern
OL,10,Fpart of Dumfries.
OL,12,FThe Galloway and West Dumfries
OL,13,Fconstituency covers towns including
OL,14,FStranraer, Castle Douglas,
OL,15,FKirkcudbright, Wigtown and the western
OL,16,Fpart of Dumfries.
OL,18,FSouth Scotland: A region of towns
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/19
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
