OL,3,CSouth Scotland: The race for a place
OL,4,Con the regional list
OL,6,FThe region is mostly rural and there
OL,7,Fare no cities. Towns and villages are
OL,8,Fspread across the area and many have
OL,9,Ftheir own distinct history and
OL,10,Fculture. They also face challenges
OL,11,Fincluding transport, access to
OL,12,Fhealthcare and a shortage of housing.
OL,14,FGretna and Gretna Green are famous as
OL,15,Fpopular wedding venues.
OL,17,FLocated right on the Border between
OL,18,FScotland and England, historically
OL,19,Feloping couples travelled there to
OL,20,Ftake advantage of Scotland's more
OL,21,Frelaxed marriage laws.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/19
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
