PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1777554668
OL,3,CSouth Scotland: The race for a place
OL,4,Con the regional list
OL,6,FCelebrant Mark Smith has been marrying
OL,7,Fcouples in Gretna for 15 years.
OL,9,FHe said: "Economically it's very
OL,10,Fimportant, probably adds something
OL,11,Flike #15m to the local economy
OL,12,Fdirectly. So even though it's doing
OL,13,Fwell the area really does need all the
OL,14,Fsupport it can get because weddings
OL,15,Fare on the decrease nationally, so we
OL,16,Fneed to be sure Gretna, Gretna Green,
OL,17,Fis able to hold its own."
OL,19,FWigtown in Galloway was officially
OL,20,Fdesignated as Scotland's National Book
OL,21,FTown in 1998.
OL,26,@qD@JOUyD@YO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/19
