OL,3,CSouth Scotland: The race for a place
OL,4,Con the regional list
OL,6,FMelrose in the Borders is the
OL,7,Fbirthplace of Rugby Sevens. The sport
OL,8,Fwas invented there in 1883 and every
OL,9,Fyear they hold an annual Melrose
OL,10,FSevens tournament which attracts huge
OL,11,Fcrowds.
OL,13,FMelrose Rugby Club president George
OL,14,FRunciman said: "We're very fortunate
OL,15,Fthat it was two butchers from up
OL,16,FMelrose way in 1883 when the club was
OL,17,Fa bit short of money, they came up
OL,18,Fwith the great idea of having seven a
OL,19,Fside rugby."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/19
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1777554668
OL,3,CSouth Scotland: The race for a place
OL,4,Con the regional list
OL,6,FNowadays, Rugby Sevens is an Olympic
OL,7,Fsport and is played all over the world.
OL,9,FGeorge added: "Melrose and Melrose
OL,10,Fsevens go together. And it was part of
OL,11,Four culture and part of the town's
OL,12,Fculture. It feels good when you win
OL,13,Fand not so good when you lose."
OL,15,FHow would the political parties better
OL,16,Fsupport the region's communities?
OL,18,FITV Border asked all the main parties
OL,19,Fstanding on the list to put forward
OL,20,Ftheir number one candidate.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/19
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
