OL,3,CSouth Scotland: The race for a place
OL,4,Con the regional list
OL,6,FMairi McAllan, SNP
OL,8,F"My great grandfather came to the area
OL,9,Fas a blacksmith in the 20s and my
OL,10,Fgreat grandmother, their family were
OL,11,Fminers at the forth, so I know this
OL,12,Farea and I have used that local
OL,13,Fknowledge and that deep care to be an
OL,14,Factive energetic representative."
OL,16,FRachael Hamilton, Scottish
OL,17,FConservatives
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G11/19
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
