PN,35212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1777554668
OL,3,CSouth Scotland: The race for a place
OL,4,Con the regional list
OL,6,F"We want to see businesses thrive, the
OL,7,FScottish Conservatives are right
OL,8,Fbehind growing the economy. We want to
OL,9,Fsee taxes cut for people, so that they
OL,10,Fcan put more money in their pocket and
OL,11,Fwe want to see businesses supported."
OL,13,FCarol Mochan, Scottish Labour
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G12/19
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1777554668
OL,3,CSouth Scotland: The race for a place
OL,4,Con the regional list
OL,6,F"So we have our policies around
OL,7,Fchildcare, around apprenticeships,
OL,8,Faround the NHS, but at the core of
OL,9,Fthem is about what will work in your
OL,10,Fcommunity and over the last five years
OL,11,FI've really worked with the party to
OL,12,Fmake sure that we can provide that for
OL,13,Fpeople."
OL,15,FDuncan Dunlop, Scottish Liberal
OL,16,FDemocrats
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G13/19
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
