SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1777554668
OL,3,CSouth Scotland: The race for a place
OL,4,Con the regional list
OL,6,F"We would trust people to make
OL,7,Fdecisions about the issues that affect
OL,8,Ftheir daily lives, we believe in
OL,9,Flocalism. There's no reason whether
OL,10,Fyou're in Hawick or Melrose or
OL,11,FWeymouth that you should not be making
OL,12,Fdecisions for your town and your
OL,13,Fpeople."
OL,15,FJamie Langan, Reform UK
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G14/19
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
