SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1777554668
OL,3,CSouth Scotland: The race for a place
OL,4,Con the regional list
OL,6,F"Reform UK wants to put more money
OL,7,Finto the pockets of hardworking people
OL,8,Facross the south of Scotland, empower
OL,9,Fcommunities to develop long-lasting
OL,10,Fand real wealth and prosperity right
OL,11,Facross the region."
OL,13,FLaura Moodie, Scottish Greens
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G15/19
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
