OL,3,CSouth Scotland: The race for a place
OL,4,Con the regional list
OL,6,F"The cost of living crisis is hard
OL,7,Fhere, that's because we have low
OL,8,Fwages. Access to public services is
OL,9,Fdifficult, especially the NHS, we want
OL,10,Fto bring dentistry for example back
OL,11,Finto NHS control and to give public
OL,12,Fservices more funding and transport is
OL,13,Fa really big issue especially the lack
OL,14,Fof affordable reliable buses and the
OL,15,Flack of trains."
